{"tid":1822743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黃色經濟圈】影藍店大頭事件，讓其自然死亡就係最佳做法","createTime":"2020-01-13T06:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T10:37:41.000Z","uid":205733,"like":61,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"94f0bf6125aabc9bb80968e778bb159092c081fe","tid":1822743,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:52:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>大家有眼睇，黃色經濟圈本身就非常成功<br />\n成功既原因係：道德高地，低成本，完全合法</strong></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>共產黨驚到甩褲，先有幾十篇文章討伐黃色經濟圈、<br />\n仲有警黑多次合作繼續搞黃店<br />\n文攻武嚇必定繼續攻擊黃色經濟圈，詳情可以追我舊post</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我個人認爲：<br />\n- 現階段共產黨發覺文攻完全無效，武嚇效果亦不大<br />\n- 所以重心就擺落心戰<br />\n- 道德爭議為新風向，讓兩方爭拗而内部擊潰黃色經濟圈<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地做法就係兩邊繼續兄弟爬山，不用爭拗<br />\n堅持理性討論，不謾駡<br />\n大多數人認爲唔合適既Option就會自然死亡，一直以來都係咁<br />\n若果只係帶風向，個浪潮好快完自我修正<br />\n繼續不同路綫不決裂，自然會勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"14ef04c1861a3ebbb642883dc7ba94f417dc43d6","tid":1822743,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:53:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b237b93506bd674c36de759d01982bfc907fc3a","tid":1822743,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:54:34.000Z","msg":"不服來辯<br />\n理性討論"},{"pid":"d94729dc2e8c3179afc3cbbdcda84330f2ebc371","tid":1822743,"uid":205733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:55:32.000Z","msg":"集體意志好處就係自我修正"},{"pid":"4304386c2777e10decfd6cd133e35ed711d08057","tid":1822743,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fd0cdcc27c5cba0b45545b7a62489b10f4ebb5e4","tid":1822743,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sc